data.text:
Wonersh One-Place Study

This site may be linked to but not duplicated in any way, wholly or in part, except for private study. I must stress that although due care has been taken I cannot guarantee the information to be accurate. Contact me if you have any further information, photographs, stories or if you find any errors I will happily correct them. Narratives of living persons are not included.

Researcher: Jan Cooper, Wonersh, Surrey, England
